With a focus on design and functionality, The Sheet Society provides customers the freedom to mix and match bedding pieces, allowing for personalized and contemporary bedroom aesthetics.

name: Medik8
description: A British skincare brand committed to providing scientifically-backed, results-driven products tailored to meet various skin concerns. Known for their "CSA Philosophy"—Vitamin C in the morning, sunscreen during the day, and Vitamin A at night—Medik8 emphasizes simplifying skincare regimens while delivering maximum efficacy. They integrate sustainable practices across their operations, such as eco-friendly packaging and ethically sourced ingredients, positioning themselves as leaders in green innovation within the beauty industry.

name: YuMOVE
description: A UK-based pet supplement company dedicated to enhancing the health and mobility of dogs, cats, and other animals. Known for its scientifically backed formulations, YuMove specializes in joint health supplements designed to support pets of all ages and activity levels. The company combines high-quality natural ingredients with rigorous testing to deliver safe and effective products that are trusted by veterinarians and pet owners worldwide. YuMove is committed to sustainability, using eco-friendly packaging and renewable resources to minimize its environmental footprint.

name: Ricola
description: A Swiss company globally recognized for its premium herbal drops and natural remedies. Founded in 1930, the family-owned business combines tradition and innovation to craft soothing products made from a proprietary blend of 13 Swiss alpine herbs. Ricola’s commitment to sustainability is at the core of its operations, from cultivating herbs through sustainable farming practices to reducing its ecological footprint with eco-conscious production methods. With a focus on quality, taste, and health, Ricola continues to provide natural solutions for throat and cough relief.

name: Timo and Violet
description: A boutique company specializing in eco-friendly, artisanal products designed to bring beauty and sustainability into everyday living. Focused on handmade goods, the brand combines natural materials with thoughtful design, offering a wide range of items such as home decor, accessories, and skincare. Each product is crafted with a commitment to minimizing environmental impact, ensuring that quality and sustainability go hand-in-hand. Timo and Violet's mission is to inspire conscious living through sustainable practices and timeless designs.

name: The Bare Home
description: A Canadian-based company specializing in eco-friendly home and personal care products. Known for their dedication to sustainability, the brand offers refillable and biodegradable solutions for everyday cleaning and personal hygiene. The Bare Home's products are made with plant-based, non-toxic ingredients that are both safe for the home and the planet. By combining aesthetics with sustainability, they aim to make eco-conscious living accessible and stylish.

name: Here I Am
description: A subscription-based company committed to empowering individuals during life’s transitions with thoughtfully curated self-care and wellness products. Designed to support mental and emotional well-being, each box is personalized with items sourced from eco-friendly and socially responsible businesses. By focusing on sustainability, inclusivity, and positive impact, Here I Am Box helps people feel seen, cared for, and celebrated during pivotal moments in their lives.

name: Perlimpinpin
description: A family-oriented brand specializing in high-quality, eco-friendly products for babies and children. With a focus on comfort, safety, and sustainability, the company offers a range of thoughtfully designed clothing, bedding, and accessories crafted from organic and sustainable materials. Based in Canada, Perlinpinpin is renowned for its timeless designs and commitment to supporting families in creating safe and nurturing environments for their little ones.

name: Zusa
description: A sustainability-driven fashion brand specializing in high-performance, eco-friendly apparel for modern professionals. Founded with the mission to create durable, stylish clothing with minimal environmental impact, Zusa incorporates innovative materials and responsible production practices into every garment. From activewear to business casual staples, Zusa delivers products that blend comfort, functionality, and sustainability, empowering individuals to look and feel great while supporting a greener planet.

name: HoldOn
description: A sustainability-focused company offering innovative alternatives to traditional plastic bags. Committed to combating plastic pollution, HoldOn Bags provides a range of fully compostable and biodegradable storage and trash bags made from renewable plant-based materials. By prioritizing eco-consciousness and convenience, HoldOn Bags empowers individuals and businesses to reduce their environmental footprint without compromising on quality or functionality.

name: MITA Eyewear
description: A trailblazing eyewear brand combining fashion, innovation, and sustainability to redefine the eyewear industry. Headquartered in Miami, MITA Eyewear is dedicated to creating stylish, high-quality frames made from recycled materials, including discarded water bottles and aluminum. With a mission to reduce environmental impact while offering premium designs, MITA Eyewear bridges the gap between sustainability and modern style, inspiring conscious consumerism.
